summary: 58th Annual Meeting of the Air Pollution Control Association. Meeting held in Toronto, Ontario, Canada on June 20, 1965. Report by Dr. C.C. Varsel, Director of Research Center at the University of Toronto. For confidential support call the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline at 1-800-273-8255 or visit http://www.suicidepreventionlifeline.org/.
